column3: >Make-up Super Long Easy Fanning False Eyelashes

column2: >Make-up Super Long Easy Fanning False Eyelashes is a makeup technique that adds long extensions to the eyelids, thus providing a more dramatic and sensual look. With the help of false eyelashes, specially designed for this purpose, the technique allows achieving an impressive and long-lasting effect.

column1:
False Eyelashes: Suitable for this effect. Made of synthetic or inorganic material, slightly crimped and flexible.
Tools: tweezers, false eyelash remover, eyelash adhesive or glue, and eyelash curler.
Application: Clean the eyelid area and apply the adhesive or glue to the false eyelashes. With the tweezers, pick up the lashes and start sticking them to the upper line of the natural lashes, carefully. For a stronger effect, stick the lashes further away, repeating the process, and try not to disturb the natural lashes. Finally, use the eyelash curler to give a fine touch to the look.
